277
00:23:05,319 --> 00:23:06,880
[SPEAKER_00] I na taj način pristupamo ženama.

278
00:23:06,880 --> 00:23:09,539
[SPEAKER_00] Naprimjer, ona kad želi ti nešto ispričati,

279
00:23:09,539 --> 00:23:10,319
