281
00:23:12,200 --> 00:23:13,200
[SPEAKER_00] To je nerazumljivo.

282
00:23:13,200 --> 00:23:15,819
[SPEAKER_00] I meni je bilo, da to cvijeće,

283
00:23:15,819 --> 00:23:17,440
