296
00:23:57,180 --> 00:24:00,720
[SPEAKER_00] I možda se evo, baš, mi smo vjernici,

297
00:24:00,720 --> 00:24:01,700
[SPEAKER_00] stalno vjera, vjera, vjera.

298
00:24:01,700 --> 00:24:04,700
[SPEAKER_00] A da vas pitam definiciju vjere, ko zna?

299
00:24:04,700 --> 00:24:06,200
[SPEAKER_00] Ajde samo dignite ruku.

300
00:24:06,200 --> 00:24:07,200
[SPEAKER_00] Di se nalazi?

301
00:24:07,200 --> 00:24:08,519
